{"tid":793712,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"2019年夏季海賊王新劇場版公開決定！！","createTime":"2018-08-25T15:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T12:06:18.000Z","uid":130563,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"37f01562d6e3aa2e7eae3ca72fc72098a57398ec","tid":793712,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T15:26:52.000Z","msg":"海賊王重大發表消息正式公佈！！<br />\n<br />\n8月25日晚空島特別篇后海賊王重大發表消息正式公佈！！2019年夏季海賊王新劇場版公開決定！！TalkOP論壇專題討論鏈接在評論裡。終於宣布啦！！！ 官方完整宣傳語【海賊王超速報，繼強者世界、Z、黃金城後的海賊王動畫20週年超大作啟動，2019年夏公開決定！！！】 2019年夏季海賊王劇場版正式宣布後，官方還安排龍珠的孫悟空和路飛互動。「今年冬天就拜託你了！悟空！」「好！交給我了！路飛！」 （注：《龍珠》第20部劇場版預定於2018年12月上映）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/232610_b636e763c3a572c3b23cb774a1cc5e4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F232610_b636e763c3a572c3b23cb774a1cc5e4a.jpg&h=23b24cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/232619_c676e780bab80f2a397d4a4bb9dde715.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F232619_c676e780bab80f2a397d4a4bb9dde715.jpg&h=3c585387&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/232627_bb769028e752744a2c897fd1e69bc5e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F232627_bb769028e752744a2c897fd1e69bc5e3.jpg&h=1c012ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/232635_8c66e857cf7816a793663e07f10a6b63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F232635_8c66e857cf7816a793663e07f10a6b63.jpg&h=06ea1211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/232643_fe2ecf76c816331806e7afa96bf6de7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fuplo